{"tid":2229553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"其實今日係當年南丫海難既全港悼念日。沒有國慶，只有港殤。","createTime":"2020-10-04T13:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T14:38:20.000Z","uid":188515,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0765c95723acc5f5a198103470f19f6b4ea2d5d3","tid":2229553,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T13:07:26.000Z","msg":"今日，係南丫海難八周年的全港悼念日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（10月4日）<br />\n當年既南丫海難，唔單止摧毀左39個家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加令死難者家屬同倖存者<br />\n刻下不能磨滅既傷疤<br />\n但目前為止，事件仍然未有答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家屬既心情不但未能平息<br />\n佢地追究事件既心結，亦依然未解開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以了解吓當年嘅慘案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n銘記着呢一個「港殤之日」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m5lD4qVNNgI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm5lD4qVNNgI&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=def03dee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m5lD4qVNNgI</a>"},{"pid":"f44c4dea6e8d69638978d874f88bdef1549e784c","tid":2229553,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T13:07:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8bddce23400b1bf1434360889500618e9eff029","tid":2229553,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T13:07:49.000Z","msg":"港殤日<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m5lD4qVNNgI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm5lD4qVNNgI&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=def03dee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m5lD4qVNNgI</a>"},{"pid":"c7b835286d2f13ff1150c5352b9aaaeb4adadd34","tid":2229553,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8e700a8d4e1a6f267e26719ebec41499c8b8d71","tid":2229553,"uid"